data_table.description: Tract-based Spatial Statistics (TBSS) Based on Brain MRI, Offspring and Generation 3, 6/2009 - 6/2014. This dataset contains fractional anisotropy (FA) measures computed from the FA skeletons for 63 JHU WM regions. The values are provided for each hemisphere (left and right) and as the average weighted by the number of voxels per region.
